 "remarks": "Beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath condo offering stylish finishes and comfortable living in a convenient Norwalk location. This move-in ready home features a bright, open-concept living and dining area with gleaming hardwood floors, a cozy fireplace, and sliding doors that bring in natural light. The renovated kitchen showcases granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, subway tile backsplash, and modern cabinetry. Upstairs, you&apos;ll find two spacious bedrooms with generous closet space and an updated full bath, while the main level includes a convenient half bath for guests. Ideally located just minutes from shopping, dining, parks, and major commuter routes including I-95, Route 7, and the Metro-North Railroad, this home offers easy access to The SoNo Collection, Calf Pasture Beach, and vibrant South Norwalk. A perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.",
